activities:
Advanced Partnerships LLC receives personal information including name, email address, mailing address, phone number, fax number, job title/position, payment card number, information about your company or business, and any other information we collect about you that by itself is not personal information but if combined with personal information could be used to personally identify you. 

Advanced Partnerships LLC may use this information to:
respond to your inquiries, and/or other requests or questions; 
enable your use of the services available on our Website;
facilitate your verification and admission into our Programs(s);
investigate and mediate disputes and complaints that you file with VeraSafe concerning a Participant in our Program(s);
contact you regarding your purchase;
collect payments from you;
deliver services purchased through our Website;
send you information and updates related to your purchase;
send you invoices;
send you email notifications which you have specifically requested;
send you email marketing communications relating to our business which we think may be of interest to you; and
send you email messages containing company news, product or service information.

You may provide us with personal information when you:  
make a purchase; 
submit a complaint or dispute concerning a business that participants in VeraSafe Program(s);
complete a survey;
submit the contact form on our website;
subscribe to blog updates;
start a live chat;
subscribe to our email notifications and/or newsletters;
register for certain services, or register and/or set up an account/profile to access, visit and/or use certain portions of our Website; and
any other transactions between you and us in relation to our website or services.
